## Mandatory Workflow Requirements

- Non-trivial work starts with `/brief`, not implementation.
- `BRIEF.md` must exist before `/workflow`.
- `BRIEF.md` must define a canonical `Slug:` line in kebab-case.
- `/workflow <slug>` may continue only when the provided slug matches `BRIEF.md`.
- `SNAPSHOT.md` is always the last artifact produced by the workflow.

